import React from 'react' import { Link } from "react-router-dom" import select from 'react-select' import DropdownInput from 'react-dropdown-input' const Place = () => { const searchNames = ['Sydney', 'Melbourne', 'Brisbane', 'Adelaide', 'Perth', 'Hobart']; return ( <>
options={searchNames} defaultValue={this.props.initialValue} menuClassName='dropdown-input' onSelect={this.handleSelectName} placeholder='Search...'
) } export default Place
